{"text": "This is the angular size of the bright central maximum.", "fibs": ["size"]}
{"text": "In travelling a distance z, the diffracted beam therefore acquires a width zλ/a due to diffraction.", "fibs": ["distance"]}
{"text": "It is interesting to ask at what value of z the spreading due to diffraction becomes comparable to the size a of the aperture.", "fibs": ["value"]}
{"text": "We thus approximately equate zλ/a with a.", "fibs": ["zλ/a"]}
{"text": "This gives the distance beyond which divergence of the beam of width a becomes significant.", "fibs": ["distance"]}
